    "description": "Nakamoto Packs Co.,Ltd. provides gravure printing services in Japan and internationally. The company offers double sided fixed position printing, coater processing, sheet printing, dry laminate, construction material decorative sheets, flexible packaging materials, special bags, rotary screen-printing processing, and non-woven fiber printing. It also provides technology clean coaters, wide-width dry laminates, high-performance clean slitters, and clean gravure printing products. In addition, the company is involved in the development of electric conduction polymer coating, special molding materials, functional films, and synthesized paper, as well as plate making activities. Further, it provides product planning, design, and marketing services. Nakamoto Packs Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1941 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
